'''''The Beat Cop's Guide to Chicago Eats!''''' is a 2010 [[paperback]] food guide by Sgt. David Joseph Haynes and Christopher "Bull" Garlington, published by Lake Claremont Press. The book examines popular [[Chicago]] cafes and restaurants frequented by Chicago Police officers.<ref>http://www.lakeclaremont.com/#!the-beat-cops-guide/c5b9</ref>

