* [[Ned Dennehy]] as Father Étienne
* [[James Joint (actor)|James Joint]] as Father Pascal
* [[Matthew McNulty]] as Guillaume, a cobbler who serves in the army under Philippe
* [[Jenny Platt]] as Jeanne, Guillaume's sister

