==Reception==
The first season of ''Versailles'' received mixed to positive reviews from critics. It holds a [[Metacritic]] rating of 55 out of 100, based on six reviews,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/versailles|title=Versailles: Season 1|website=Metacritic|accessdate=September 28, 2016}}</ref> and an 80% rating on [[Rotten Tomatoes]], with an average score of 6.56 out of 10, based on 10 reviews.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/versailles/s01/|title=Versailles: Season 1 (2015-2016)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=April 3, 2018}}</ref>

